    "updated_at": "2015-05-21T18:42:08Z",
    "body": "_So_, it turns out that we were calling out to `app.exit` instead of `app.quit`. I can't find any documentation on this method, but modifying all of our calls to use quit make `localStorage` persist as expected. I think we can close this one out. :sweat_smile: \n"
